    <item>
      <title>软银计划在日本发行 35 亿美元债券，增加巨额交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/softbank-group-plans-to-offer-latest-jumbo-bond-in-yen-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团公司正计划在本国日元市场发行最新的巨额债券，如果成功，这家科技集团将成为今年全球债务市场上最大的亚洲企业借款人之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/softbank-group-plans-to-offer-latest-jumbo-bond-in-yen-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 02:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>激进对冲基金 Elliott 增持江森自控 10 亿美元以上股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/elliott-said-to-build-1-billion-plus-stake-in-johnson-controls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，激进投资者埃利奥特投资管理公司(Elliott Investment Management)在工业巨头江森自控国际公司(Johnson Controls International Plc)中建立了大量头寸，但该公司的业绩落后于同行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/elliott-said-to-build-1-billion-plus-stake-in-johnson-controls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 01:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将在首尔峰会上推动企业提高人工智能模型的安全性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-19/uk-to-push-firms-on-safety-in-ai-models-at-seoul-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府表示，将利用本周在韩国举行的一次重要峰会，进一步推动降低人工智能风险，让企业有责任负责任地开发人工智能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-19/uk-to-push-firms-on-safety-in-ai-models-at-seoul-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
